Title: Maintaining the Barricade
Description:
It's all I can do to keep this shield up under the barrage these shadowflame drakes are putting out.

Thin their ranks before we're pinned down for good.
ObjectivesText: Slay or knock Primal Nightflames from the air with Whirling Surge.

Objectives.Text: Primal Nightflames knocked to the ground or slain
